cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image style transfer. It may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves the development and evaluation of algorithms. The graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories are also possible as the paper deals with image rendering and manipulation.
